title: Hiroshige Seasons Boxed Note Cards
description:
Hiroshige's expertly rendered, beautiful, and traditional artwork is reproduced here for our museum-quality notecard collection.

Enjoy visions of the past created by Japanese artist Hiroshige.

  • Dimensions: 4.75 x 5.6 x 1.4 in.
  • Materials: Magnetic closure. Sturdy, reuseable box, ideal for keepsakes
  • 20 notecards and envelopes, 4 each of 5 images.
